    "module": "module TopModule (\n    input [3:0] in,\n    output [3:0] out_both,\n    output [3:0] out_any,\n    output [3:0] out_different\n);\n\n    // out_both: Each bit indicates if both current bit and its left neighbor are 1\n    assign out_both[3] = 1'b0; // No left neighbor\n    assign out_both[2] = in[2] & in[3];\n    assign out_both[1] = in[1] & in[2];\n    assign out_both[0] = in[0] & in[1];\n\n    // out_any: Each bit indicates if either current bit or its right neighbor are 1\n    assign out_any[0] = 1'b0; // No right neighbor\n    assign out_any[1] = in[1] | in[0];\n    assign out_any[2] = in[2] | in[1];\n    assign out_any[3] = in[3] | in[2];\n\n    // out_different: Each bit indicates if current bit is different from its left neighbor\n    // Wraparound: in[3] is considered to have in[0] as left neighbor\n    assign out_different[0] = in[0] ^ in[3];\n    assign out_different[1] = in[1] ^ in[0];\n    assign out_different[2] = in[2] ^ in[1];\n    assign out_different[3] = in[3] ^ in[2];\n\nendmodule"
